HEADWORD: Inebriant
<hw>In*e"bri*ant</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Anything that intoxicates, as
opium, alcohol, etc.; an intoxicant.</def> <rj><au>Smart.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

